    "comment": "This proposal directly addresses a critical gap in Cardano's interoperability by delivering a zero-knowledge bridge with open-source smart contracts, protocol documentation, and a proof-of-concept deployment. It enables secure, trust-minimised asset and message transfers with other blockchains, removing reliance on centralised validators. The vendor has proven cryptographic and Aiken smart contract expertise, and the project is part of the approved 2025 Cardano budget. Funding aligns with ecosystem priorities for cross-chain connectivity and future zkRollup capabilities."
